<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>Robert Jan Hogerbrugge's Portfolio: Sales Professional going webdevelopment</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper wrapper_padding clearfix">
      <div class="col-1 about homepage_content">
        <h2> About </h2>
        <hr>
        <img id="profile_pic" src="/assets/rj.png" alt="HTML5 Icon" style="width:150px;height:150px;">
        <p> After 10 awesome years in sales and business development I felt it <br>
        was time for a change in my career. In a 4 month sabbatical I overthought <br>
        my career and tried to figure out what gives me joy in life and how I <br>
        would like to spend the next 10 years of my <a href="#"> life. </a> </p>

        <p> I have spent a month learning the basics of programming languages such <br>
        as HTML, CSS, Python and Ruby. The process gave me so much joy that I <br>
        applied for a traineeship with Codaisseur to become a junior developer. </p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-2 homepage_content">
          <h2> My Projects </h2>
          <hr>

          <% @projects.each do |project| %>
            <h3><%= link_to project.title, project %> </h3>
            <p class="date"> <%= project.created_at.strftime("%A,%b, %d") %> </p>
          <% end %>

          <div class="home_pagination">
            <span class="previous_page disabled">
            Previous</span>
            <em class="current">1</em>
            <a rel="next" href="#">2</a>
            <a class="next_page" href="#">Next</a>
          </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col3 homepage_content">
          <h2> Blog posts </h2>
          <hr>

          <% @articles.each do |article| %>
            <h3><%= link_to article.title, article %></h3>
            <p class="date"> <%= article.created_at.strftime("%A,%b, %d") %> </p>
          <% end %>

            <div class="home_pagination">
              <span class="previous_page disabled">
              Previous</span>
              <em class="current">1</em>
              <a rel="next" href="#">2</a>
              <a class="next_page" href="#">Next</a>
            </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
